#cinema.home
  .container
    .row
      .col-xs-12
        #cinemacarousel.carousel.slide{"data-ride" => "carousel"}
          %ol.carousel-indicators
            %li.active{"data-slide-to" => "0", "data-target" => "#cinemacarousel"}
            %li{"data-slide-to" => "1", "data-target" => "#cinemacarousel"}
        
          .carousel-inner
            .item.active.spriteowl
              .row
                .col-sm-6.col-xs-12.startslidemodule-in-left
                  .logo
                    %h2 Spriteowl
                    %h3 Photoshop extension
                  .title Export your Photoshop Sprites to PNG and CSS, LESS, SASS/SCSS or Stylus code
                  .btnarea
                    %a.btn{title: "Spriteowl", href: "http://spriteowl.owl-stars.com"} Find out more
          
                .col-sm-6.preview.hidden-xs.startslidemodule-in-right
                  =image_tag "cinema/spriteowl-extension-colors.png", :alt => "", :class => "img-responsive"

            .item.cssowl
              .row
                .col-sm-6.col-xs-12
                  .logo
                    %h2 Cssowl
                    %h3 Mixin library
                  .title Cssowl is a mixin library with support for LESS, SASS/SCSS and Stylus
                  .btnarea
                    %a.btn{title: "Cssowl", href: "http://cssowl.owl-stars.com"} Find out more
              
                .col-sm-6.preview.hidden-xs
                  =image_tag "cinema/cssowl-code.png", :alt => "", :class => "img-responsive"
#main
  .section.info
    .container
      .row
        .col-xs-12.col-md-10.col-md-offset-1.intro
          %h2.introTitle
            With our Owl-Stars product series we improve the workflow between designers and developers or make live easier for people who do both. 
  
  .section.products.bgdark
    .container
      .row
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
          .product.spriteowl.slidemodule
            .head
              .logo
                %h2 Spriteowl
                %h3.hidden-xs.hidden-sm Photoshop extension
            .price
              Only $
              %span.bigPrice> 20
            .info
              Spriteowl is a Photoshop extension that takes over the boring part when working with sprite images and CSS.
            .features
              %ul
                %li.check Retrieves x, y, width and height info of all sprite elements for you
                %li.check Exports retina ready PNG files and all required media queries of your Photoshop sprite file
                %li.check Supports preprocessors LESS, SASS/SCSS & Stylus
            .btnarea
              %a.btn{title: "Spriteowl", href: "http://spriteowl.owl-stars.com"} Find out more

        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
          .product.cssowl.slidemodule
            .head
              .logo
                %h2 Cssowl
                %h3.hidden-xs.hidden-sm Mixin library
            .price
              %span.bigPrice Free
            .info
              Cssowl is a mixin library that work with the Photoshop extension Spriteowl to help you developing easier and faster.
            .features
              %ul
                %li.check LESS, SASS/SCSS & Stylus support
                %li.check Open source
                %li.check Easy to use
            .btnarea
              %a.btn{title: "Cssowl", href: "http://cssowl.owl-stars.com"} Find out more


  .section.about
    .container
      .row
        .col-xs-12.col-md-8.col-md-offset-2.intro
          %h2.introTitle About Owl-Stars

      .row
        .col-sm-6
          %p
            The <strong>Owl-Stars product series</strong> enable you to <strong>develop websites and applications faster and easier</strong>.
            We are currently working on more cool stuff, so <strong>stay tuned and subscribe to our newsletter</strong>!
